		<title>Mayo Clinic collaborates on ARPA-H award to develop a bioprinted liver for acute liver failure</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-collaborates-on-arpa-h-award-to-develop-a-bioprinted-liver-for-acute-liver-failure/
		
		<dc:creator><!--[CDATA[Lynda De Widt]]--></dc:creator>
		<pubdate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 15:12:11 +0000</pubdate>
				<category><!--[CDATA[Biotherapeutics]]--></category>
